title: Intake Air Filter, Universal Car 3" Carbon Fibre Cold Air Filter Feed Enclosed Intake Induction Pipe Hose Kit
features: 【COMPATIBLE】- Air Filter Induction Kit with flexible cold air feed hose, carbon fibre air induction system designed to fit most of cars. Produced according to the professional standard, you can be purchased and used with confidence.
【HIGH QUALITY】- Air Filter with carbon fibre shell, beautiful appearance and lightweight, good noise reduction property and heat insulation. Keep heat to minimum and maximize the air flow.

【FUNCTION】- Intake Air Filter can effectively increase horsepower and improve the gas mileage, make the oil combustion complete and decrease the oil consumption. Reduce engine's carbon deposit and prolong it's service life.

【EXCELLENT PERFORMANCE】- Intake Induction Filter adopt airbox design, it can store a plenty of fresh air and avoid blocked by insufficient air intake while oil return. Extremely improving the smoothness of driving. With washable and reusable filter cartridge, economical and practical.
NOTE - Our Induction Kit does not include intake turbine.For some cars,you may need an additional pipe.
